{"type": "article", "id": 5914, "title": "MSDS Studio 家具作品", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-05T07:54:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233825fUdukx0FrWVb3jnA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自加拿大的设计公司 MSDS Studio 在今年的斯德哥尔摩家具展上带来了全新的木制家具系列与灯饰作品，出自 Jessica Nakanishi 与 Jonathan Sabine 两位设计师之手。该系列包含有一个沙发床、床垫、半开放式橱柜、椅子以及吊灯等。可以堆叠起来的床垫能够自然地形成一个枕头，带有铝制面板的橱柜既保留了封闭空间，也留出了可用来作为展示与陈列部分的空间，A型靠椅做成了可堆叠设计的样子，小木偶台灯与锥形吊灯则是简单中透着俏皮。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233823iVJcpLnvwauor2Y5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233823dPKAMvHgjD4XCkzo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233823zQMHIqYDj7KNaXgp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233824hwCubaRS1E2OsBqy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233824zmXJNFRDp4AgelYP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}